I had the same problem with the clutch cable. Make sure you route the cable
the same way as the old one. If you don't you either end up with it too long
or too short. Also, if you removed the arm under the bus that controls the
clutch petal, make sure that is installed correctly. That will also make the
cable seem as though it is too long.

Bob


