Ok, today I removed the new cable. Cable looked fine.

Put it next to my old cable, same length.

Reinstalled new cable. Put a couple of washers on the bowden tube to get a
more accurate bend.

Checked pedal assembly. Ok.

I'm 95% sure there is nothing wrong with the cable, bowden tube, or pedal
assembly.

